    M300 to rate blacklist
    - LP: #433801

  [ Upstream Kernel Changes ]

  * PM: Make warning in suspend_test_finish() less likely to happen
    - LP: #464552

 -- Stefan Bader <stefan.bader@canonical.com>  Wed, 28 Oct 2009 21:21:02 +0000

